HEADWORD: Underfurrow
<hw>Un`der*fur"row</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To cover as
under a furrow; to plow in; <as>as, to <ex>underfurrow</ex> seed or
manure</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

